Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护接受了上级贵族霞大路家的公主琉璃千代的保镖一职
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与企图篡夺霞大路家的云井尧觉所派出的刺客展开了激战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在激战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:02:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护打败了暗杀部队的首领贯井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但石田和茶渡却受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着受了重伤的两人而动摇了的琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了中止这场纷争而一个人回到了尸魂界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来琉璃千代早就知道云井要暗杀自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护等人为了继承权问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闯入了琉璃千代的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌乱 镇定点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢擅自闯入贵族的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂队长 请您听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场婚礼和新首领就任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些本身就是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们让你感到孤独无助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想保护你却反而将你逼入了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道你一直忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你也不需要全部一人承担下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你已经下定决心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要听云井的话的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是霞大路家真正的首领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一人无法完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好 犬龙也好 猿龙也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚 井上 石田 茶渡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你只要做你认为对的事情就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢对奴家如此无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还愣着干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抓住这些乱党贼子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再扩大骚动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快把他们逮住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 猿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿龙 好强大的破坏力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他至今都未曾解放过斩魄刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚 琉璃千代人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你逃掉的 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开奴家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴家不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作点啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是琉璃千代的未婚夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙现在有些异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会察觉不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云井那家伙一定对琉璃千代做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我什么也...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...是假的吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃她...难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底知不知道自己在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箇中缘由容我日后相告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您让我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为你是个值得敬重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我是看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别狡辩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大前田副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟敢把我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情我才不想知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木大人 快趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 我绝不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这样 可千万别放手啊 猿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放烂漫吧 红枝垂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个琉璃千代是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...你一定要相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种谎话你到底要说到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用空手搏击的战斗你还不太习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还想再吃点苦头嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽敌螯杀 雀蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想尽可能不解放斩魄刀解决事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌舞吧 袖白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次之舞 白涟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些死神要追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出去的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是逃进宅邸里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将还能行动的人集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重编队伍去追他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩等下再办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在优先抓捕黑崎和朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要派人进入府邸内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云井尧觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些贼子会由我府上的人赶出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们跑出来就请您抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是对上等贵族最基本的尊重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们来了 大家都很慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菅之木愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是琉璃千代的未婚夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的琉璃到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃她发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你镇定一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是琉璃的未婚夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护琉璃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了你刚才的一番话 我有所感悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和琉璃的婚事是家里擅自决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我从第一次见到她的时候开始就喜欢上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是菅之木愁大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃的立场艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这连我也看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是让琉璃她那么孤独无助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在帮她也为时不晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起保护琉璃千代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首先得从这里逃出去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是府邸周围应该有碎蜂他们包围着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云井还没有来联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道他们家族是多大的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,府邸实在是太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞这么大到底要干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大前田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这些不知轻重的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说刚才抓住的人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好绑着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好盯着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护他们可能会来救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会自己闯入我们的包围圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后门发现黑崎一护和朽木露琪亚的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓了菅之木愁大人做人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不但破坏婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还敢挟持人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎蜂队长 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你让开道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:16:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木和一护竟然会...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个... 黑崎一护是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 天贝队长并不认识他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做死神代行的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神代行？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样的人存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护和朽木露琪亚两人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挟持了菅之木家之子 菅之木愁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在瀞灵廷内逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在二番队正在进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考虑黑崎一护的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为有必要增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样 那就由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他和各位有很深的交情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定很难下手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准天贝队长的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀞灵廷内紧急戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以二番 三番队为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对死神代行黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及十三番队朽木露琪亚进行追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 总队长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞大路家的重臣云井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然请求我们出动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又不让我们进入府邸内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及他异样的警戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和多处可疑点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他与黑崎一护之间似乎有些过节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉良 已有联络了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都已经做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对你们来说 可能有点难下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是为了守护尸魂界秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备出动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是霞大路家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有报告过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话的话你就直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个... 我一直在想该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还是告诉队长比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上这之前我看到贵船三席
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进出霞大路家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我问他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却否定自己进出那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想队长可能还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前贵船三席也曾有过可疑的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无犹豫地对同伴刀剑相向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗结束时不知在记录什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他平和的表面完全相反的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个贵船怎么可能会...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些事情我以前都没有听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在贵船进出的霞大路家又发生事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人在隐藏着自己和霞大路家的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定有某些...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下定论还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他和霞大路家有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也还不能说他有什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种状态下有这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪你会觉得有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事你和别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和谁都没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件可能还有很多内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要暗中注意贵船的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一有问题就马上来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先去抓住黑崎一护
